STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Edelbarto PADILLA, a/k/a Leo Del Monte, Leo Delmonte, Eric Cortez, Raul Hernandez, Herberto Padilla, Michael Landon, Erickson Paz, Ericson Pazarielo, Ericson Pzarielo, Michael L. Pazarielo, Eric Santana, Michael Laurara, Leo Deleon, and Leo Demich, Defendant-Petitioner. C-777 September Term 2018
081911 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 4, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004601-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
